WEBVTT

1
01:07:20.760 --> 01:07:23.890 
我不知道
I had no idea.

2
01:07:23.960 --> 01:07:26.830 
她做得滴水不漏
She did everything right.

3
01:07:26.900 --> 01:07:31.460 
但是，她疏忽了一点
And then, she made one little mistake.

4
01:07:31.540 --> 01:07:33.700 
她把包落在了候诊室
She left her purse in the waiting room.

5
01:07:33.770 --> 01:07:36.670 
别管伦理道德
Forget ethics.

6
01:07:36.740 --> 01:07:38.270 
你有五分钟
You got five minutes.

7
01:07:38.340 --> 01:07:39.710 
你知道我在哪
You know where I'll be.

8
01:07:39.780 --> 01:07:42.470 
我没有信得过的人了
I don't trust anyone else.

9
01:07:42.550 --> 01:07:44.450 
只有你了
It has to be you.

10
01:07:44.520 --> 01:07:47.420 
那些信件，克雷
The mail, Clay.

11
01:07:47.490 --> 01:07:49.720 
她还是用她的名字
She still had her mail.

12
01:07:49.790 --> 01:07:52.050 
等等，乔纳森？
Wait. Jonathan?

